{"tid":142232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有請周綺萍！廢中：辭職因為「做得唔開心」","createTime":"2017-03-03T14:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T01:30:20.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3254881f697e78bd5acd111569dddbc0dd2e536d","tid":142232,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:47:46.000Z","msg":"候選人曾俊華接受《星島日報》專訪時直言，辭職時仍未有參選決定，又指辭職其中一個理由是「做得不開心」"},{"pid":"06308e18e0f2fef104ca6868c07f5b6970cc3b45","tid":142232,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"被問到為何做了近5年才不開心，曾俊華則形容是「去到一個點」，覺得不能做下去。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華在訪問中指，辭職不是因為參選，有很多其他事情，其中一樣是做得不開心，但拒絕透露有甚麼具體事情令他堅持辭職。"},{"pid":"f064c7b4913268f9db1015e9d6bd986edfa25c83","tid":142232,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T23:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1841071f553ffce2f4f87e89de01c0f6e1a6bf2","tid":142232,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T23:02:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"658ad6560b53730ae4fce2d856ecbb27117be50b","tid":142232,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T23:39:18.000Z","msg":"689根本一早就睇薯片唔順眼<br />\n佢本身財爺個位係比劏房<br />\n不過比支那bam左姐<br />\n之後咪比個濕鳩局長佢做囉"},{"pid":"c1a1609779af91ba98f774e8f211cbdb0fa7e1e4","tid":142232,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T23:50:28.000Z","msg":"而家啲50後, 感情大過理性"},{"pid":"3eecc3ad45904ecec263ffb799f792b7b7cc6de4","tid":142232,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T00:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家啲50後, 感情大過理性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家d 50後唔崖得。"},{"pid":"95ff329a787a20e1213fcc4151d1d90ceef2cf6f","tid":142232,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T00:16:09.000Z","msg":"周綺萍：葉劉 心頭高... 廢中不應心頭過高"},{"pid":"e56888726ac15a4cf4d8ea5121df91ba6206e779","tid":1